    "text": "Home\nAbout Us\nFood\nDrinks\nOccasions\nStay\nContact Us\nThe\nMEXICO INN\nBook a table\nPlease note, we close our booking system at 10.30am for on the day bookings. To check our availability please call 01736710625\n\"The Mexico’s shelves heave with well-thumbed cookbooks, making the place pleasantly cluttered. Service is lovely: warm and knowledgeable. It’s as if they’re actually happy to see you.\"\nGrace Dent, The Guardian\nRead the article\nWhat's on\nWobbly Wednesday\nSunday roast\nBook a table\n Gift Cards\nTreat someone you love to a meal at The Mexico with one of our gift vouchers. Simply fill out the form and the e-voucher will be delivered to an inbox of your choosing instantly.\nGift Vouchers\nStay with us\nOur two stylish self contained flats can be booked individually or together - perfect for families or friends who want to stay close but need a bit of space.\n  Book with us direct by emailing stay@themexicoinn.com\nTake a closer look\nWE LOOK FORWARD TO SEEING YOU\nThe Mexico Inn \n4 Riverside, Long Rock\nPenzance, Cornwall TR20 8JD\n  Monday – Saturday  11:30am – Late\nSunday  12pm – Late\n  Tel: 01736 710625\nEmail: info@themexicoinn.com\n01736 710625 \nInfo@theMexicoInn.com\nAll imagery supplied by: Flux Kernow\n© 2020 The Mexico Inn\nJoin Our Mailing List\nSubscribe now",
